OL,3,CGrandparents found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Ctoddler Ethan Ives-Griffiths
OL,6,FA couple have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering their two-year-old grandson.
OL,9,FEthan Ives-Griffiths died from a
OL,10,Fcatastrophic brain injury, two days
OL,11,Fafter he collapsed in the living room
OL,12,Fat the home of his grandparents
OL,13,FMichael and Kerry Ives, in Flintshire
OL,14,Fin North Wales.
OL,16,FA trial at Mold Crown Court, lasting
OL,17,Fmore than five weeks, heard the boy
OL,18,Fwas severely underweight and
OL,19,Fdehydrated when he died, with 40
OL,20,Fvisible marks on his body.
