OL,3,CGrandparents found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Ctoddler Ethan Ives-Griffiths
OL,6,FThe pair stared straight ahead as the
OL,7,Fverdict was read out after nearly
OL,8,Fseven hours of deliberations. In
OL,9,Faddition to murder they were also
OL,10,Ffound guilty of child cruelty.
OL,12,FEthan's mother Shannon Ives, who was
OL,13,Fliving with her parents at the time,
OL,14,Fwas found guilty of causing or
OL,15,Fallowing his death and child cruelty.
OL,17,FEthan Ives-Griffiths would have been
OL,18,Fsix if he had lived but North Wales
OL,19,FPolice said he didn't stand a chance
OL,20,Fafter moving into his grandparents'
OL,21,FGarden City home in late June 2021.
