OL,6,FHe was initially living there without
OL,7,Fhis mother Shannon but she also moved
OL,8,Fin a few weeks later.
OL,10,FThroughout the nearly six week trial,
OL,11,FCCTV was played to jurors showing
OL,12,FEthan picked up by his grandfather and
OL,13,Fgrabbed like a "rag doll" and a "bag
OL,14,Fof rubbish".
OL,16,FOn occasions both Kerry and Shannon
OL,17,FIves were captured standing nearby but
OL,18,Fneither stepped in to help or stop the
OL,19,Fabuse.
