OL,6,FEthan was also prevented from seeing
OL,7,Fsocial workers and medical advice was
OL,8,Fnot sought by his mother or
OL,9,Fgrandparents when he collapsed but
OL,10,Fregained consciousness on 13th August,
OL,11,Fjust 24 hours before he collapsed
OL,12,Fagain in the living room of Kingsley
OL,13,FRoad.
OL,15,FThe two-year-old died days later, on
OL,16,F16th August 2021, at Alder Hey
OL,17,FChildren's Hospital in Liverpool
