OL,3,CGrandparents found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Ctoddler Ethan Ives-Griffiths
OL,6,FOpening the case last month, Caroline
OL,7,FRees KC, prosecuting, said Ethan was
OL,8,Fexposed to "casual brutality" and,
OL,9,Faccording to a medical expert, would
OL,10,Fhave experienced "distress, pain and
OL,11,Fmisery in the days and weeks prior to
OL,12,Fhis death".
OL,14,FJurors were shown CCTV from outside
OL,15,Fthe home, of Michael Ives carrying the
OL,16,Fyoungster by the top of his arm. They
OL,17,Fwere also shown footage of Michael
OL,18,FIves seeming to mock and aim a
OL,19,Fhosepipe at him on a trampoline as he
OL,20,Fstruggled to stand.
