OL,6,FBoth Michael and Kerry Ives told the
OL,7,Fjury nothing happened in the moments
OL,8,Fbefore Ethan collapsed, but the court
OL,9,Fheard medical experts believed his
OL,10,Fhead injury was caused by deliberate
OL,11,Fuse of force, which may have included
OL,12,Fforceful shaking.
OL,14,FThe prosecution said the "overwhelming
OL,15,Fexpert evidence" suggested the fatal
OL,16,Finjury was caused within minutes of
OL,17,Fhis collapse.
OL,19,FJudge Mr Justice Martin Griffiths said
OL,20,Fall three would face jail sentences
