OL,6,FShannon Ives was bailed for sentencing
OL,7,Fon October 3 2025. Her parents are
OL,8,Fback behind bars and will be sentenced
OL,9,Fthe same day.
OL,11,FHe said "there's only one sentence for
OL,12,Fmurder and that's imprisonment for
OL,13,Flife. Thats what I'm bound to pass and
OL,14,Fwill pass but I must consider a
OL,15,Fminimum term."
OL,17,FHe also warned Shannon Ives that she
OL,18,Ffaced a "substantial prison sentence".
